{"tid":1229254,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"貿戰影響浮現　6月整體物業成交登記挫兩成","createTime":"2019-06-16T00:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T04:38:28.000Z","uid":174649,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c767732e1fcab8c33cb6d1beb8497b3074ff2fec","tid":1229254,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:52:45.000Z","msg":"美聯物業援引土地註冊處資料指，6月首13日整體物業暫錄2,749宗成交登記，較5月份同期3,440宗減少約20.1%，數字反映5月份中美貿戰升級對樓市的影響正逐步浮現。<br />\n<br />\n期內一手私人住宅的成交登記跌幅顯著，暫錄626宗，較5月同期808宗下跌22.5%。<br />\n<br />\n至於二手住宅，6月首13日共錄1,614宗成交登記，按月跌約16.5%。"},{"pid":"4af72ac86c0d92bcc8beecde49e6adb2cf6cd8c5","tid":1229254,"uid":28067,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:54:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾美聯 係撚貿易戰呀<br />\n送中條例先無人買乍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9aa76d87a9a5a743f923d099257b5b778e0b06c","tid":1229254,"uid":122318,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4af72ac86c0d92bcc8beecde49e6adb2cf6cd8c5","tid":1229254,"uid":28067,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:54:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾美聯 係撚貿易戰呀<br />\n送中條例先無人買乍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:29:32.000Z","msg":"不能説的秘密<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c2cfbbe6a16909978aa3510dc7f5fa66fa291f","tid":1229254,"uid":112720,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"4af72ac86c0d92bcc8beecde